M|dev|- What breaks if this fails at 2am? Is there a failure path that cascades?
M|dev|- Will this work in the Vercel serverless environment (no persistent mem, no SWC binary on Linux)?
M|dev|- Am I adding a pattern I will regret at 10× traffic?
M|dev|Correct or cut everything found in Pass 2. Run `npx tsc --noEmit` before delivering. If it fails, stay in Pass 3.
M|dev|> Populated from ses errors. Each entry: [date] — pattern — rule that prevents recurrence.
M|dev|- **SSE over WebSockets** — simpler, works with Vercel serverless. `/api/claude` streams via `ReadableStream`.
M|dev|- **All external calls via /api/ route handlers only** — API keys never touch client components. Non-negotiable.
M|dev|- **Supabase for all persistent data** — localStorage is ephemeral UI only (active tab, scroll, prefs).
M|dev|- **Prompt caching on system prompts** — `/api/claude` wraps systemPrompt in `cache_control: { type: 'ephemeral' }`.
M|dev|- **War Room hard cap: 2 specialists** — `.slice(0, 2)` enforced in `/api/team-chat`. Never raise this.
M|dev|- **Nate model: claude-haiku-4-5-20251001** — downgraded from Sonnet 2026-03-23. Applies in `agents.ts` + `briefing/route.ts`.
M|dev|- **TypeScript in Linux VM** — `npx tsc --noEmit` only. `npm run build` won't work (SWC binary is Windows-only).
M|dev|- **Cookie `yvon_active_venture`** — vtr source of truth, server-readable. All new pages must read from it.
M|dev|- ❌ API calls from client components — sec violation
M|dev|- ❌ File-write instructions in API system prompts — mem write-back is CLAUDE.md only
M|dev|- ❌ localStorage for data — fails on cache clear
M|dev|- ❌ Hardcoded colors in components — CSS variable tokens from globals.css only
M|dev|- ❌ Hardcoded soc handles / GA property IDs — per-vtr env vars only
